{"tid":690461,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4 pro club] D1 pro club 球隊招人踢VPL S19 及 電競聯賽","createTime":"2018-06-05T01:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T08:16:27.000Z","uid":78671,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9aca0b8913c197e976acad5e33a0db5b9d14616","tid":690461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"球隊因賽制問題缺席了上季HKVPL S18 賽事，今季已報名參加HKVPL S19 &amp; HKEFPCL 電競聯賽 S2 賽事<br />\n<br />\n長遠目標係挑戰傳統勁旅，故希望能吸納更多好波之人。<br />\n<br />\n現招以下位置好手補強（<span style=\"color: red;\">左右兩閘、中堅及龍門</span>），希望一齊夾好波。<br />\n<br />\n踢法：理想係打造一支踢法上模仿巴塞或曼城的傳控球隊，故球隊希望球員有在隊友旁邊現位（形成三角形）幫波的意識，及中前場球員必須擁有高控球能力（有能力在極短時間內猜散各比賽強隊的迫搶，比人迫兩下就甩波便不了）<br />\n不是單純踢跑狗反擊/高q大棍燒味，目標係要踢出有球隊特色及技術的踢法。希望能邀到有共同理念及能力的選手一齊合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每晚會10點左右進行試腳。<br />\n<br />\n如有意試腳，請add telegram <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ps4fifa_pro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fps4fifa_pro&d=Zt5PrfE02W2MKJ332E7kZ7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=46587a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ps4fifa_pro</a><br />\n<br />\nthanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99871662715d0b35f9b06a7d3bc99df74a2039d","tid":690461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"今晚10點鐘左右有場安排試腳<br />\n暫只收中堅/左右閘/龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274b3acfac2287e9b31901be18744fd8a163b09c","tid":690461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"今晚11點鐘電競聯賽熱身賽<br />\n歡迎加入試腳<br />\n暫只收中堅/左右閘/龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275c8496a9d9f56d1cbae22eea0aab58dd6502a1","tid":690461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"今晚11點鐘電競聯賽熱身賽<br />\n歡迎加入試腳<br />\n暫只收中堅/左右閘/龍門<img sr